                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17820911-118-off587 t17820911-118-crimeloc589"></join> the 22d of July, between nine and ten in the evening; I laid hold of him, and he threw it down; I took him; he was never out of my sight; it was an India one, value 4 s.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I did not take it; I have been troubled with fits.</p>
